ing only progressive core\nswelling at temperatures intermediate to both transition temperatures, thus\npromoting linear swelling behaviour.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 16 Nov 2020 09:52:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-11-17"}
