o classify radio-fre-quency\nsignals encoding 8x8 pixel handwritten digits pictures. The spintronic neural\nnetwork recognizes the digits with an accuracy of 99.96 %, equivalent to purely\nsoftware neural net-works. This MAC implementation offers a promising solution\nfor fast, low-power radio-fre-quency classification applications, and a new\nbuilding block for spintronic deep neural net-works.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 16 Nov 2020 11:55:25 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 5 Apr 2021 11:39:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-04-06"}
